  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p><fr:link href="/schm-HZ25/" title="Affine morphisms" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-HZ25/" display-uri="schm-HZ25" type="local">Affine morphisms</fr:link> are evidently <fr:link href="/schm-BH0E/" title="Quasi-compact morphisms" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-BH0E/" display-uri="schm-BH0E" type="local">quasi-compact</fr:link>. In particular, morphisms between affine schemes are quasi-compact.
